  "response": "Sure! Here are some popular ecchi yuri anime series:\n\n1. **\"Strawberry Panic!\"** - This series combines school romance with dramatic twists and features deep connections between the female characters.\n\n2. **\"Citrus (Saburouta)\"** - It's a romantic drama revolving around stepsisters who develop an intense and complicated relationship, with plenty of ecchi moments.\n\n3. **\"Yuruyuri\"** - A light-hearted comedic series that focuses on the daily lives and romantic entanglements of a group of middle school girls.\n\n4. **\"Netsuzou Trap -NTR-\"** - This series explores themes of deception and forbidden love, with significant ecchi elements and yuri relationships.\n\n5. **\"Kanamemo\"** - A mix of slice-of-life and comedy, focusing on the interactions between the female characters, with occasional ecchi undertones.\n\nPlease note that the term \"ecchi\" often denotes mature content with sexual undertones, so these series may not be suitable for all audiences.",
